title: Mini-Ep 280: Norm-Core House Tour
itunes:title: Mini-Ep 280: Norm-Core House Tour
description:
Kate caves and goes deep on the Goop products and Doree takes a plunge into cleaning up her yard. Then, listeners literally pull over to send a text affirming Kate’s butter snacking habit, pass their phone to their partner to weigh in on the generic brand makeup convo, and encourage the discussion around norm-core house content.
